#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:10
msgid ""
"Video wallpaper for Linux. Written in Python. 🐍\n"
"\n"
"Hidamari 日溜まり 【ひだまり】 (n) sunny spot; exposure to the sun"
msgstr ""
"Linux 向けの動画ウォールペーパー。Python で書かれています。🐍\n"
"\n"
"ひだまり【日溜まり】(名) 日の当たる暖かい場所"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:76
msgid "Quick toggles"
msgstr "クイック切り替え"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:93
msgid "Autostart after login"
msgstr "ログイン後に自動起動"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:106
msgid "Video frame can be applied as system wallpaper, look great in GNOME"
msgstr "動画のフレームをシステム壁紙として適用でき、GNOME で美しく表示されます"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:108
msgid "Apply static wallpaper"
msgstr "静止画壁紙を適用"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:121
msgid ""
"Automatically pauses playback when maximized window or full screen mode is "
"detected"
msgstr ""
"ウィンドウの最大化やフルスクリーンを検出すると自動的に再生を一時停止します"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:123
msgid "Pause when maximized window"
msgstr "ウィンドウ最大化時に一時停止"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:136
msgid ""
"Automatically mutes playback when maximized window or full screen mode is "
"detected"
msgstr "ウィンドウの最大化やフルスクリーンを検出すると自動的にミュートします"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:138
msgid "Mute when maximized window"
msgstr "ウィンドウ最大化時にミュート"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:162
msgid "Volume control"
msgstr "音量調整"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:223
msgid "Static wallpaper blur radius"
msgstr "静止画壁紙のぼかし半径"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:266
msgid "Open config file"
msgstr "設定ファイルを開く"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:280
msgid "About Hidamari"
msgstr "Hidamari について"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:339
msgid ""
"<span size=\"x-large\"><b>Local Video</b></span>\n"
"Videos located in Hidamari folder"
msgstr ""
"<span size=\"x-large\"><b>ローカル動画</b></span>\n"
"Hidamari フォルダー内の動画"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:355
msgid "Refresh"
msgstr "更新"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:380
msgid "Open Hidamari folder"
msgstr "Hidamari フォルダーを開く"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:432 src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:755
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "適用"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:452
msgid "Local Video"
msgstr "ローカル動画"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:465
msgid ""
"<span size=\"x-large\"><b>Streaming</b></span>\n"
"Videos from streaming services"
msgstr ""
"<span size=\"x-large\"><b>ストリーミング</b></span>\n"
"ストリーミングサービスの動画"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:500
msgid "<b>Streaming URL</b>"
msgstr "<b>ストリーミング URL</b>"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:541
msgid "💡\tThis feature uses <i>yt-dlp</i> as backend"
msgstr "💡\tこの機能はバックエンドに <i>yt-dlp</i> を使用します"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:555
msgid ""
"😉\tTry playing any YouTube video! <a href=\"https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-"
"dlp/blob/master/supportedsites.md\">Supported sites (yt-dlp)</a>"
msgstr ""
"😉\tYouTube の動画を再生してみましょう！<a href=\"https://github.com/yt-dlp/"
"yt-dlp/blob/master/supportedsites.md\">対応サイト (yt-dlp)</a>"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:570 src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:697
msgid "Hint"
msgstr "ヒント"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:591
msgid "Streaming"
msgstr "ストリーミング"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:605
msgid ""
"<span size=\"x-large\"><b>Web Page</b></span>\n"
"Set a web page as wallpaper"
msgstr ""
"<span size=\"x-large\"><b>ウェブページ</b></span>\n"
"ウェブページを壁紙に設定"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:640
msgid "<b>Web Page URL</b>"
msgstr "<b>ウェブページ URL</b>"

#: src/hidamari/assets/control.ui:681
msgid ""
"💡\tCheck this website for some really amazing examples!\n"
"\t<a href=\"https://alteredqualia.com/\">https://alteredqualia.com/</a>"
msgstr ""
"💡\tこのウェブサイトで素晴らしい例をチェックしてみましょう！\n"
"\t<a href=\"https://alteredqualia.com/\">https://alteredqualia.com/</a>"

